  "detailed_description": "Astroderps is a fun puzzle game for all ages. The objective is to solve puzzles that guide your Astroderps to safety. You can move blocks to create a path, extinguish fires, build bridges, and deflect projectiles. Timing and dexterity is key to get your Astroderps safely from one portal to the next. <br />\r\n<br />\r\nThere are multiple levels for users to solve, each more challenging than the previous one. Are you up for the challenge?",
